b'Adding shame to sadness is a pretty toxic cocktail. It\xe2\x80\x99s hard enough to deal with sadness, depression, or any type of anxiety without the added societal expectations. It\xe2\x80\x99s important & more healing to meet ppl where they\xe2\x80\x99re at - EMPATHY - than to try & paint everything rosy. 2/3'

b'Rose-Colored Boy is a song about feeling pressured to look at the world with blind optimism when you actually feel very hopeless about the world & your part in it. there is so much social pressure to be (or appear to be) \xe2\x80\x9chappy\xe2\x80\x9d that we can actually feel shame when we aren\xe2\x80\x99t. 1/3 https://t.co/STiu3U44eZ'
